    <item>
      <title>台湾致力于恢复对中国影响的军事审判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/taiwan-works-to-restore-military-trials-citing-china-influence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾总统莱·钦（Lai Ching-te）表示，政府将努力让军事法庭在和平时期开展业务，并宣布加强了与中国交流的规则，强调了人们对北京在岛上及其武装部队的行动的日益关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-13/taiwan-works-to-restore-military-trials-citing-china-influence</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Mar 2025 07:03:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
